er what and where you spend your points on, because your choice will depend on the fate of the entire colony! The Promised Land, a brave new world , the hole nation – all this lies in your hands! Become a true leader, a chosen one, a father of nation! Guide your colony to the victory of the modern superpower!We collected all the best that is in games of this genre, arched by exciting mini-games and carefully turned it into the deep and breathtaking adventure!•	Complete freedom of play•	More than 10 hours of gameplay•	Up to 50 player-controlled characters•	Huge, untamed world to explore•	Step-by-step tutorial						
